Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.11,0:22:34.87,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(150,100)}但回首而望 只有風的呼嘯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:37.75,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(150,100)}Don't let me down, Don't make me confuse
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.83,0:22:42.54,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(150,100)}使我不斷充斥著絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.75,0:22:46.34,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(150,100)}Escape from here!! It's like a nightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:48.97,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(150,100)}會追上的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:56.31,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(150,100)}無論夢想、理想、或是熱情 還是會被消除
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:23:02.81,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(150,100)}哀傷的日子 何時才能迎來終點？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:11.70,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(150,100)}不停迷茫 不斷掙扎 即使如此仍不願放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:15.24,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(150,100)}即使滿身傷痕 在這隻手上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.41,0:23:18.70,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(150,100)}仍有絕不會消逝的星光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.74,0:23:25.84,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(150,100)}墮天而下的光芒 現在仍遠遠照耀著那處
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:32.34,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(150,100)}無論幾次都會伸出手 即使現在無法描繪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.34,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(150,100)}信念一定能化為力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.43,0:23:38.43,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(150,100)}閃耀吧 Shooting STAR
